<h1>Two Posts on &#8216;Daltonite Revisionism&#8217;</h1>
<p>Author: strugglesessions</p>
<p>Publish Time: 2023-02-26T10:00:00+00:00</p>
<p>Modified Time: 2023-02-08T15:05:34+00:00</p>
<p>Description: Note: the following two essays were published by a former Tribune supporter going by René. They provide a slightly different viewpoint and analysis of the revisionism of the crcpusa to what we have…</p>
